						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and incomplete. It seems to record a gift of land to meet the expenses of daily offerings to the deity in the temple of Tirumālpēṟuḍaiyār, made by a lady by name Araṅgaṉ Periyāḷ, the wife of a local Veḷḷāḷa resident.</p>						

